{"change_summary":"No additional code edits were required in this round. The prior implementation already satisfied the approved review for bead-to-task run linkage, so I left the code unchanged and revalidated the milestone-record path.","outstanding_risks":["Task-run completion still updates lineage, snapshot, and journal files separately, so a crash between writes could leave those artifacts temporarily inconsistent until repaired."],"steps":[{"description":"Reviewed the approved validation output and confirmed there were no follow-up amendments or requested fixes to apply for the milestone task-run lineage changes.","order":0,"status":"completed"},{"description":"Revalidated the existing implementation with formatting, milestone_record unit tests, and clippy without making further code changes.","order":1,"status":"completed"}],"validation_evidence":["`cargo fmt --all --check` completed successfully.","`cargo test --lib contexts::milestone_record` passed with 65 tests.","`cargo clippy -- -D warnings` completed successfully."]}